profile:
Welcome to Signature Cleaning Services. We are a Top Rated Winnipeg Cleaning Company servicing all of Winnipeg, Headingley, East St. Paul, West St. Paul, St. Andrews and everything in between. 

We are not a franchise, we are a local home grown company founded on integrity, accountability and excellence. 
We hire only employees that we train to deliver our Signature Cleaning Method that is earning 5 Star Reviews from customers every single week. 
Our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee means you'll LOVE your clean or we'll come back and fix it. 
Our 99% Reliability Rate means we will clean your home on the day it's scheduled. 
Our Quality Assurance Program ensures we deliver Consistency and Excellence. 
All our people are Bonded  Insured and we maintain valid Background Checks for each employee. 

Service SO GREAT You'll See STARS!
